'''晨星公司'''（{{lang-en|Morningstar, Inc.}}；{{NASDAQ|MORN}}），是[[美國|美國]]一家對全球資本市場與基金有獨立投資研究的權威評級機構，其總部位於[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]]，也是全球從事基金評級業務的唯一一家上市公司。該公司是由美國[[億萬富翁|億萬富翁]]等級企業家{{tsl|en|Joe Mansueto|喬・曼索托}}於1984年所創立。晨星公司在29個國家設有業務，其研究和建議對[[資產管理|資產管理]]行業具有影響力，而晨星分析師的積極或消極的建議可以使資金流入或流出基金<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ft.com/join/licence/a6338099-2efb-499b-a00e-0090b29b31ef/details?ft-content-uuid=e02d2768-22d2-11e4-8dae-00144feabdc0|title=Dentons UKMEA LLP|website=Financial Times|access-date=2021-02-25|archive-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301063725/https://www.ft.com/join/licence/a6338099-2efb-499b-a00e-0090b29b31ef/details?ft-content-uuid=e02d2768-22d2-11e4-8dae-00144feabdc0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/5026242|title=Star Power: The Effect of Morningstar Ratings on Mutual Fund Flow|first1=Diane|last1=Del Guercio|first2=Paula|last2=Tkac|date=2001-02-01|journal=Journal of Financial and Quantitative Analysis|volume=37|via=ResearchGate|doi=10.2139/ssrn.286157|hdl=10419/100799|access-date=2021-02-25|archive-date=2020-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200424170423/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/5026242_Star_Power_The_Effect_of_Morningstar_Ratings_on_Mutual_Fund_Flow|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2020年9月30日，該公司通過其資產管理部門管理的資產超過2,440億美元<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bridgehousecanada.com/investment-managers/morningstar/|title=Morningstar Associates Inc. | Bridgehouse Asset Managers|access-date=2021-02-25|archive-date=2019-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112074553/https://bridgehousecanada.com/investment-managers/morningstar/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ft.com/join/licence/a6338099-2efb-499b-a00e-0090b29b31ef/details?ft-content-uuid=b9dcfc38-d355-11e6-b06b-680c49b4b4c0|title=Dentons UKMEA LLP|website=Financial Times|access-date=2021-02-25|archive-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301063728/https://www.ft.com/join/licence/a6338099-2efb-499b-a00e-0090b29b31ef/details?ft-content-uuid=b9dcfc38-d355-11e6-b06b-680c49b4b4c0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該公司還為專業投資者提供數據平台和軟件，其中包括 Morningstar Direct 和 Morningstar Advisor Workstation。

==公司沿革==
===成立以前===
1982年，當{{tsl|en|Joe Mansueto|喬・曼索托}}回顧了他向幾位知名基金經理要求的共同基金年度報告時，萌生了晨星計劃（Morningstar）的想法<ref name="incarticle">{{cite web | title=Everything I Know, I Learned from Warren Buffett, Corporate Culture Article – Inc. Article | url=http://www.inc.com/magazine/19990701/811.html | access-date=May 3, 2007 | archive-date=2021-01-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125223350/http://www.inc.com/magazine/19990701/811.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，直到哈里斯協會（Harris Associates）擔任股票分析師一年後，看到基金行業和潛在競爭對手近在咫尺，他才確信機會就在這裡<ref name="incarticle" /><ref name="mstaradvisorarticle">{{cite web | title=Joe Mansueto and Bill Nygren: The Importance of Having Conviction | url=http://morningstaradviser.com/articles/comments.asp?docId=4490 | access-date=May 3, 2007 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045029/http://morningstaradviser.com/articles/comments.asp?docId=4490 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
===公司成立===
1984年，{{tsl|en|Joe Mansueto|喬・曼索托}}在芝加哥的一間臥室的公寓中創立晨星（Morningstar），初期投資為80,000美元<ref name="usatodayarticle">{{cite news | title=USATODAY.com – Can he turn magazine bust into a boom? | url=https://www.usatoday.com/money/companies/management/2005-11-14-mansueto_x.htm | access-date=May 3, 2007 | work=USA Today | first1=Mindy | last1=Fetterman | date=November 14, 2005 | archive-date=2011-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622115959/http://www.usatoday.com/money/companies/management/2005-11-14-mansueto_x.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。晨星這個名字取自亨利·戴維·梭羅（Henry David Thoreau）所著的《沃爾登》（Walden）中的最後一句話: “太陽不過是晨星”<ref name="usatodayarticle" /><ref name="usatodayarticle2">{{cite news | title=A star is reborn after shake-up | url=https://www.usatoday.com/money/perfi/funds/2001-02-12-mstar.htm | access-date=May 21, 2007 | work=USA Today | date=February 12, 2001 | archive-date=2011-05-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110523060827/http://www.usatoday.com/money/perfi/funds/2001-02-12-mstar.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1998年，晨星公司與[[軟銀集團|軟銀集團]]在日本成立了一家合資企業。1999年7月，晨星公司獲得來自軟銀集團的9100萬美元投資，軟體銀行取得晨星公司20％的股份<ref name="usatodayarticle2" /><ref name="nytimessoftbank">{{cite news | title=Company News; Softbank says it will invest $91 million in Morningstar | url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C03EEDE153CF93AA35754C0A96F958260 | access-date=May 3, 2007 | work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] | date=July 9, 1999}}</ref>。

===公開上市與擴張===
2005年5月3日，晨星進行了[[首次公開發行|首次公開發行]]，以每股18.50美元的價格發行了7,612,500股<ref name="ipopricing">{{cite web | title=Morningstar Press Release | url=http://corporate.morningstar.com/US/asp/subject.aspx?xmlfile=174.xml&filter=PR4113 | access-date=May 3, 2007 | archive-date=2011-07-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719081024/http://corporate.morningstar.com/US/asp/subject.aspx?xmlfile=174.xml&filter=PR4113 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。晨星的上市方式值得注意。他們選擇遵循Google的腳步，並使用[[公開發行|公開發行]]的方法而不是傳統方法。這使個人投資者可以對股票的價格進行出價，並允許所有投資者享有平等的機會。

2006年，晨星收購伊博森公司 (Ibbotson Associates, Inc.)，一家投資研究機構<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://newsroom.morningstar.com/newsroom/news-archive/press-release-details/2005/Morningstar-Inc-to-Acquire-Ibbotson-Associates---Combines-Ibbotsons-Expertise-in-Asset-Allocation-and-Morningstars-Expertise-in-Security-Selection-and-Investment-Research/default.aspx|title=Morningstar, Inc. to Acquire Ibbotson Associates - Combines Ibbotson’s Expertise in Asset Allocation and Morningstar’s Expertise in Security Selection and Investment Research|first=Morningstar|website=Morningstar}}</ref>。2007年，晨星收購[[標普全球|標普全球]]的全球基金數據業務<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.integrity-research.com/morninstar-acquires-sp-mutual-fund-database/|title=Morninstar Acquires S&P Mutual Fund Database|website=Integrity Research Associates|access-date=February 27, 2007|archive-date=2020-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218142940/http://www.integrity-research.com/morninstar-acquires-sp-mutual-fund-database/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年，晨星收購信用評級機構 Realpoint，並開始為機構投資者提供結構性的信用等級和研究<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748703580904575131620249936264|title=Morningstar to Buy Credit Rater Realpoint|first=Anusha Shrivastava And Joan E.|last=Solsman|date=March 19, 2010|via=www.wsj.com|access-date=2021-02-25|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206034141/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748703580904575131620249936264|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，晨星以1,830萬美元收購 Old Broad Street Research Ltd. (OBSR)，一家英國基金研究，評級和投資諮詢服務提供商。收購完成後，命名為 Morningstar OBSR<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://newsroom.morningstar.com/newsroom/news-archive/press-release-details/2010/Morningstar-UK-Ltd-Acquires-London-based-Old-Broad-Street-Research-Ltd-OBSR-Premier-Provider-of-Fund-Research-Ratings-and-Investment-Consulting-Services-in-the-United-Kingdom/default.aspx|title=Morningstar UK Ltd. Acquires London-based Old Broad Street Research Ltd. (OBSR), Premier Provider of Fund Research, Ratings, and Investment Consulting Services in the United Kingdom|first=Morningstar|website=Mornginstar}}</ref>。

2014年，晨星收購 ByAllAccounts, Inc.，一家金融應用創新數據聚合技術提供商<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/morningstar-inc-acquires-byallaccounts-inc-provider-of-innovative-data-aggregation-technology-for-financial-applications-253432591.html|title=Morningstar, Inc. Acquires ByAllAccounts, Inc., Provider of Innovative Data Aggregation Technology for Financial Applications|first=Margaret Kirch|last=Cohen|website=CISION}}</ref>。

2016年，晨星以大約2.25億美元收購 {{tsl|en|PitchBook Data|PitchBook Data}} 的剩餘所有權<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.seattletimes.com/business/technology/morningstar-buys-seattle-startup-pitchbook-for-180-million/|title=Morningstar buys Seattle startup PitchBook in $225 million deal|first=Rachel|last=Lerman|website=Seattle Times|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2017-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620090620/http://www.seattletimes.com/business/technology/morningstar-buys-seattle-startup-pitchbook-for-180-million/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年9月，晨星公司宣布已任命庫納爾·卡普爾（Kunal Kapoor）為首席執行官，自2017年1月起生效，曼索托同時擔任執行主席。，

2019年，晨星以6.69億美元收購全球第四大信用評級機構 [[DBRS|DBRS]]。收購完成後，[[DBRS|DBRS]] 與晨星信用評級業務結合<ref name="#2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/morningstar-looks-to-expand-ratings-business-with-dbrs-deal-11559151916|title=Morningstar Looks to Expand Ratings Business With DBRS Deal|first=Gunjan|last=Banerji|website=WSJ|access-date=2021-02-25|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127191826/https://www.wsj.com/articles/morningstar-looks-to-expand-ratings-business-with-dbrs-deal-11559151916|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年，晨星達成收購 {{tsl|en|Sustainalytics|Sustainalytics}} 的協議，一家專門研究環境、社會和治理（ESG）見解的研究和評級公司<ref>{{cite web |url=https://newsroom.morningstar.com/newsroom/news-archive/press-release-details/2020/Morningstar-to-Acquire-Sustainalytics-and-Expand-Access-to-ESG-Research-Data-and-Analytics-for-Investors-Worldwide/default.aspx |title=Morningstar to Acquire Sustainalytics and Expand Access to ESG Research, Data, and Analytics for Investors Worldwide |access-date=2021-02-27 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202054456/https://newsroom.morningstar.com/newsroom/news-archive/press-release-details/2020/Morningstar-to-Acquire-Sustainalytics-and-Expand-Access-to-ESG-Research-Data-and-Analytics-for-Investors-Worldwide/default.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年，晨星同意收購 PlanPlus Global，一家總部位於加拿大的財務計劃和風險評估軟件公司<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.zhitongcaijing.com/content/detail/278891.html |title=晨星(MORN.US)将收购财务计划及风险评估软件公司PlanPlus Global }}</ref>。

2021年，晨星宣布將以3500萬英鎊收購澳大利亞財富管理平台 Praemium (ASX: PPS) 的英國及國際（包括澤西島、香港和迪拜）業務。<ref>{{cite web|title=Morningstar to Buy Praemium's UK, International Business for GBP35M|url=https://www.zvstus.com/article/news/1/d0df7ffffe8222e093b918a4760d0000.html|website=尊嘉金融|publisher=marketwatch|access-date=December 21, 2021|archive-date=2022-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220213204512/https://www.zvstus.com/article/news/1/d0df7ffffe8222e093b918a4760d0000.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2022年，晨星宣布將以6億至6.5億美元收購[[標普全球|標普全球]]的 Leveraged Commentary & Data (LCD) 業務，一家專門提供槓桿貸款市場數據公司<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://seekingalpha.com/news/3820436-morningstar-plans-to-buy-leveraged-commentary-data-for-up-to-650m|title=Morningstar plans to buy Leveraged Commentary & Data for up to $650M|first=Max|last=Gottlich|website=Seeking Alpha|access-date=2022-04-22|archive-date=2022-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220414124700/https://seekingalpha.com/news/3820436-morningstar-plans-to-buy-leveraged-commentary-data-for-up-to-650m}}</ref>。

